# Design Document for DrugNcoin Project

## Overview

This document outlines the design and implementation plan for the DrugNcoin project, a mem-coin based on the TON blockchain. The project includes the development of tokenomics, a website with pre-sale options, payment integrations, and smart contracts for the token.

